.\" Manpage for simple_shell hsh.
.\" Contact 6386@holbertonschool.com, or 6378@holbertonschool.com in order to correct errors.
.SH SYNOPSIS FOR INTERACTIVE MODE
Use “./hsh” to show prompt. 
Command synopsis: [command] [options]
.SH SYNOPSIS NON INTERACTIVE 
echo "[command] [options]" | ./hsh
.SH DESCRIPTION
this simple_shell is a recreation of “sh” command interpreter that has been made using C language. This version can execute any command that points to an executable file. 
It includes files on the same directory ("./[filename]"), files with the full direction ("/bin/ls") and files that can be found in the PATH environment variable ("ls"). 
